# Cards

@callout .info
	Cards are layout primitives.
@end callout

@row
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@row
			@card .accent
				Accent
			@end card

			@card
				Default
			@end card
		@end row
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

